cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.SI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a novel ensemble model that aims to improve the diversity of base learners and reduce the training error. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The proposed algorithm is designed to optimize the ensemble model and improve its performance. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The proposed method can be applied to improve the performance of computer vision models that use ensembles. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper proposes a new measurement of diversity (exclusivity) and a customized algorithm to optimize the ensemble model. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The proposed method can be applied to improve the performance of ensemble models used in social and information networks.
